place_info.title: Massage Envy
place_info.address: 4383 Arden Wy, Sacramento, CA 95864

reviews.snippet: I have been at the Arden way location twice now. I have to agree that this location has no concept of customer service. I was given credit from my husband to use. When I booked it, I clearly specified that I would be using my husband's credit and they confirmed that all was good. And I would only pay the $10 transfer fee. When I checked out after my massage, i was asked to pay $80. Then I was advised that credits to the same person could only be transferred once every six months. This is not about money but rather lack of professionalism and communication. I am not new to massages but every therapist has a different style. Do not recommend this place to anyone.

response.snippet: Thanks for sharing your most recent experience with us, SNisha. Please reach out to the franchised location’s manager at (916) 971-3689 so they can address this further.
